title: Beautiful House in Winder!
posting_body: Beautiful 2 story home in quiet neighborhood near The Chimneys golf course.
Home features upgraded kitchen experience with stainless appliances and gorgeous LVP flooring.
Large downstairs den is perfect for entertaining.
Deck off the main level is perfect for relaxing with friends.
Upstairs you will find spacious master with ensuite and 3 additional bedrooms.
This home has zoned HVAC system for your comfort and to the benefit of your wallet and it sits on a full unfinished basement - perfect for storage or playtime.
This home accepts pets on a case by case basis with a non-refundable pet fee.
Available at the beginning of August!
Home is tenant-occupied through the end of July.
We will begin showings on August 4 with available move-in around August 8.
